[I] Plasmoids for KDE Plasma - main package

[T] KDE Plasmoids module is a collection of additional Plasma data engines
[T] and widgets (applets). It is part of the official KDE distribution.
[T] This package contains Plasma data engines and widgets (applets). Install
[T] this package if you want to use plasmoids from the KDE Plasmoids module.

